wikipedia_page.main: Katherine Mills (born 1983) is an English magician and mentalist. She had her own show, Katherine Mills: Mind Games, on cable channel Watch. She also appeared in the BAFTA Children's Award–winning show Help! My Supply Teacher's Still Magic.

response: *Katherine Mills performed on Mind Games, a British TV show.
The magicians featured are James Went, Katherine Mills, Fergus Flannigan and John Archer. The series was created and executive produced by Objective Productions by Anthony Owen.
